{"tid":2038081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毛主席教大家如何打遊擊戰","createTime":"2020-05-27T10:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T10:47:54.000Z","uid":335967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9c1f463fcd0a3e521395ea5cf85141847a7d66","tid":2038081,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:39:13.000Z","msg":"毛主席遊擊戰秘訣:「<span style=\"color: red;\">敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n敵進我退: <br />\n面對精良裝備嘅敵人， <span style=\"color: red;\">切忌陣地戰</span>、攻防戰， 一定要喺敵人包圍網/ 布袋陣形成前就要走， 要記住<span style=\"color: red;\">撤退都係戰略嘅一種</span>，走唔代表係懦夫。 避過圍捕先可以長打長做。<br />\n<br />\n敵駐我擾:<br />\n敵人駐守喺某一個地方，就要<span style=\"color: red;\">善用干擾戰術</span>， 例如心理戰， 喺<span style=\"color: red;\">樓上</span>不停辱罵/ 叫囂/空襲( 樓上最安全，捉你唔到)。 目的係令敵人恐懼同埋心理上覺得煩厭， 因為就算敵人回罵，如果上面不斷有人挑釁又捉你唔到， 其實長時間都會頂唔順。 另外，<span style=\"color: red;\">空襲</span>係極有效，因為敵人唔知襲擊喺邊度嚟，喺地面駐守巡邏好容易分心。<br />\n<br />\n敵疲我打:<br />\n敵人冇可能守哂每一條街， 邊條街冇人守就搞邊度， 敵人嚟就走， 敵人撤走就再搞過。 目的<span style=\"color: red;\">令敵人疲於奔命</span>。<br />\n<br />\n敵退我追:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前提係要克服敵人一沖前大部分人本能性逃走</span>嘅心理障礙， 否則絕對唔建議咁做。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 我只係同大家回顧共匪喺國共內戰嘅戰術，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同香港抗爭絕對冇任何關係</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b749099b46b69976ee0bd8db8b3dde30809184","tid":2038081,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579a4310d20eb5d81202815cb7d2adb86199b00b","tid":2038081,"uid":36578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:43:29.000Z","msg":"推..."},{"pid":"da88801f981cc78cd8174cf9901434ce2c5ef20d","tid":2038081,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e2052bec71ad16d27612642659a99daae96fc1","tid":2038081,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8507be4f5beac48b7764f0b7c76e6182479d1ddb","tid":2038081,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:47:12.000Z","msg":"香港獨立"},{"pid":"dfdd356bf441db225135b9f1c6c685e6cfdc3c60","tid":2038081,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:47:24.000Z","msg":"唯一出路"},{"pid":"61c6bc35a04e6b27f360240008200042503b0b21","tid":2038081,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:47:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eef32db3f5bb637883348138aadbc04d13e3e6b","tid":2038081,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68136e876ca2b68e2dc188659a75061329eb06b","tid":2038081,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}